{"tid":60551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯將對美國帶有侵略性的新制裁做出回應","createTime":"2016-12-30T14:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T15:38:33.000Z","uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1639e222e8d1efea44d34a813bec5706aafc0be0","tid":60551,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"&lt;莫斯科：俄羅斯將對美國帶有侵略性的新制裁做出回應&gt;<br />\n　　美國總統歐巴馬總統29日下令，驅逐35名俄國外交和情報人員，並關閉兩棟俄國在美國境內的建築物。華盛頓認為，俄羅斯在2016年總統選舉期間，參與入侵美國網絡，繼而影響美國總統大選。<br />\n　　對此，俄國總統新聞秘書表示，「歐巴馬在其任期最後三周採取如此制裁措施，帶有急遽的破壞性。」、「普丁總統目前不急著與美國開展對話，我們也拒絕回應此番毫無根據的指控。面對如此制裁，俄國也必將採取相對的回應。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tass.com/politics/923402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Fpolitics%2F923402&d=%2FydTJhKqhqhTf7DS1pevZJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=05903e2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://tass.com/politics/923402</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1216715118409736&amp;id=740553002692619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1216715118409736%26id%3D740553002692619&d=%2FydTJhKqhqhTf7DS1pevZJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7ff7d30e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1216715118409736&amp;id=740553002692619</a>"},{"pid":"33d4ae89a0060661ec19e8fc07980061044bffdc","tid":60551,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"黑白臉<br />\n<br />\n克里姆林宮宣佈，俄總統普京已駁回外長提出驅逐35名美外交官的建議，表示不會對奧巴馬政府最新舉動作出任何回應行動，等待川普上台後美政府的舉動才再作決定。普京還邀請美國駐俄外交官的子女參加克里姆林宮的新年晚會。<br />\n<br />\n--... <a href=\"https://t.co/qWk3GkOKtI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqWk3GkOKtI&d=%2FydTJhKqhqhTf7DS1pevZJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8ad9d363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/qWk3GkOKtI</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.sputniknews.cn/politics/201612301021527579/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.sputniknews.cn%2Fpolitics%2F201612301021527579%2F&d=%2FydTJhKqhqhTf7DS1pevZJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=1e64fee5\" target=\"_blank\">http://big5.sputniknews.cn/politics/201612301021527579/</a>"},{"pid":"3c41791539bda24fb8ca374ccf5d4ed79bbc3f13","tid":60551,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:23:10.000Z","msg":"俄佬又學埋支那d衰野，淨係得把口"},{"pid":"de309e62b50c38e446b238cceb0fd4fbad793d3e","tid":60551,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俄佬又學埋支那d衰野，淨係得把口</blockquote><br />\n都唔係嘅 係普京落命令話等埋Trump上任先算"}]}